  <h2>Key Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Python 3.14 with Flask 3.1 for lightweight HTTP routing</li>
    <li>Gunicorn WSGI server for multi-worker concurrency</li>
    <li>psycopg2 for efficient PostgreSQL connectivity</li>
    <li>PostgreSQL stored procedures for server-side business logic</li>
    <li>Consistent throughput under strict resource constraints</li>
  </ul>

